(23, 23, 'course-categories', 'Success and Happiness are no accident. Every successful person has a map or a model. NLP is a system of discovering, modeling and installing those maps and models in others so they can achieve the same results.\r\n\r\nBecause NLP is a system of observing and acquiring new behaviour, it can be used to help acquire that which is important to you.\r\nAreas that are covered for discussion and demonstration include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Removing: barriers, self doubt, limiting beliefs, fear, phobias &amp; depression.</li>\r\n	<li>How to achieve brilliance in :\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Business Relationships</li>\r\n	<li>Sales</li>\r\n	<li>Personal Relationships</li>\r\n	<li>Learning &amp; Memory</li>\r\n	<li>Happiness &amp; Wealth</li>\r\n	<li>Health and vitality</li>\r\n	<li>Sports Performance\r\nand more ...</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis is seminar of discovery.  Discovering the why, what and how of NLP.   It is an evening of demonstrating the effectiveness, speed and power of NLP to bring about lasting positive change in a persons life.', 0, 15),
(24, 24, 'course-categories', 'Sales Mastery is about discovering you or your teams true potential. It is about taking the stress out of the whole sale process and understand how to truly interpret the subtle messages give out by all of us and turning them into sales.   The sales process is made up of a series of links, like a chain.  The final sales result is determined not by your strongest link but unfortunately by the weakest.  Most people are great at those things the like doing and are generally very good a avoiding those things or subject that cause any form of discomfort. The end result is people strengthen their strengths and maintain their weakness and as a result performance frequently remains relatively constant.<p><p>\r\nSales Mastery is multifaceted, firstly it looks at improving communication dramatically by understanding both conscious and unconscious messages given by a client. Secondly it reduces the process of selling to a series of simple to follow steps and as a result lets an individual know precisely where they are in the selling cycle at any moment in time. Finally and possible most important of all is the removal of limiting beliefs and conflicting values that act as road blocks it an individuals success. Sales Mastery is divided into 3 independent subject. These subject can be taught independently or as a 3 day training program.<p><p>\r\n <strong>Module 1. Closing By Design</strong> The Closing By Design module is a process of learning how to, what to observe and most important of all, how to utilise the information once collected. For the person that takes the time to practice Closing By Design success is guaranteed.<p><p> <strong>Module 2. Making it impossible to say &#039;No&#039;</strong> Everyones decision making process is unique. Expecting one technique to work on everyone is ridiculous. Module 2 is about getting the customer to tell you their unique decision making process. With this information in hand closing become as simple as painting by numbers.\r\n<div class="gmail_quote">\r\n<div><strong>Module 3. Creating a Super Salesman Mindset. </strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\nSales managers often lament that  20% of the sales staff produce 80% of the result. If they could only get more of the staff to perform like the top few, business would be great. This situation is brought about by a salespersons belief about themselves and the profession. Imagine for a moment your sales staff could be hypnotised into being high performers. Removing limiting self belief and limiting decision about the profession. So that they all produce great results.', 0, 21),
(25, 25, 'course-categories', '<strong>The bottom-line is the bottom line!</strong><P></P>\r\n\r\nWhat we teach in Closing by design is customer neural profiling. Sound complex but it is very straight forward. People that have trained with us have described it as totally unfair advantage over their competitors.<P></P>\r\n\r\nClosing is not just the final stag of a sale. It is a crucial part of every step the sales process. Closing is used at the point of getting the appointment. It is used in the very process of discovering and qualifying a lead. It is used in establishing the relationship, the building of trust, presenting of information, service or product and finally the asking for the deal itself.<P></P>\r\n\r\nWhat is imperative to understand is that everyone has their own unique way of being convinced. Discover this unique process and you will close more deals than ever before. The Dynamic Mind Works - Closing by Design focuses on how the customer thinks and makes decisions. Of course the most important decision of all is how do they say, "Yes" to your produce or service rather than your competitor!', 0, 5),
