(27, 27, 'course-categories', 'The Neuro Linguistic Coaching Program (NLCP) is designed to empower you with focus, creativity, strength and accountability to achieve the consistent results you demand in the most valuable areas in your life.\r\n\r\nNLCP is profoundly separate to what you may already know of: life coaching; counselling; mentoring; motivational coaching; advising; or various traditional therapeutic methods of self improvement and understanding. NLCP addresses your personal goals; breaks addictive habits and behaviours; improves business clarity, performance and success; transforms relationships; and strengthens your connection with others; as well as facilitating many other positive outcomes. In short, NLCP succeeds in closing the loop holes that other coaching modalities miss.\r\n\r\nIn many cases, you are not living the life you want due to your misaligned self-beliefs or values, which unbeknownst to you, may well contradict each other. Often you may find that your goals require you to go one way, but your beliefs and values are pulling you another way. Therefore if you are feeling lost, depressed, angry, or frustrated in life, it is likely you are experiencing this internal struggle between two conflicting internal thought processes. This is not a recipe for a healthy, balanced and happy future!\r\n\r\nYour NLCP coach we go through the process of exploring your beliefs, both about yourself and about your situation. Is the belief you are harbouring helping you to achieve the desired outcome, or preventing you? Similarly, what values do you possess on a conscious or subconscious level that are holding you back from reaching your full, untapped, potential?\r\n\r\nPeople are unique, and so are their problems. An NLCP coach has an inbuilt flexibility when designing a session for a client, resulting in a highly personalized, well tuned and incredibly successful solution.\r\n\r\nNLCP is about identifying the belief or values you may not know exist, but that are impacting your life deeply every day. Together we will work to understand and explore your ‘blue print’, to provide you with the necessary tools to achieve your desired outcome. These is achieved through the following:\r\n\r\nBreaking down beliefs or values that are holding you back.\r\nHelping your mind move on from incidents in your past that are preventing possibilities in the present\r\nCreate new empowered beliefs and values\r\nUnderstand your ‘blue print’ to transform your state to an empowered state within minutes\r\nCreating rituals that will help you achieve your outcome\r\nYour coach holding you accountable to take masterful action\r\nAdd untold value to yourself, and as a direct result, add value to those around you\r\nNLCP uses the most advanced technology available in psychology today to help you achieve your goals, both personal and professional, and allow you to follow the life path of your choosing.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">Ready to ask questions or book into your coaching program? Contact us here.  Ask for Coach Niro!</a>', 0, 4),
