(97, 1, '2014-12-05 01:21:05', '2014-12-05 01:21:05', 'NLP Enthusiasts take note!  Learn NLP from the comfort of your living room.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in learning NLP but not interested in attending a full course just now then this is the next best thing!\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">NLP Practitioner DVD set</span></h4>\r\n<strong>22 disk DVD set - Full classroom experience.  $750 inc. GST\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>37 hours of NLP training.  Live demonstrations, bonus techniques.</strong>\r\n\r\nThe pricing of this comprehensive DVD set reflects the volume of information included and the uniqueness of course content delivery.\r\n\r\nThe DVD set can be used in a variety of ways: a source of reference, learning, modelling, practice.  It is an educational resource and has been produced in a way to keep costs to a minimum so more customers can access this product.  Similar products on the market are priced at over $1,200.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">Contact us to order.</a>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">NLP Master Practitioner</span></h4>\r\n<strong>20 disk DVD set - Full classroom experience.  $950 inc. GST</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Over 44 hours of a real NLP Master Practitioner classroom training.</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">Contact us to order.</a>', 'NLP DVD sets', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dynamicmindworksnlpdvdsets', '', '', '2015-01-12 09:21:20', '2015-01-12 09:21:20', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/?post_type=services&#038;p=97', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(98, 1, '2014-12-05 01:21:47', '2014-12-05 01:21:47', '<p class="introduction2">NLP is a popular abbreviation used for Neuro Linguistic Programming.</p>\r\nAs the name suggests, NLP is the ability to affect or change the nervous system through the use of language. NLP is not magic, but it comes pretty close. For any individual that has a desire to change or achieve more, NLP holds the keys to a new, wealthier, healthier and happier future. NLP in many ways hold the keys to becoming the type person you dream of.What does this really mean?As human beings, we are living, breathing organisms with highly evolved nervous systems. Every experience an individual has in life is processed through this nervous system. How we learn, experience, remember, think, breathe, move, relate, stay healthy and even reproduce are all controlled through this system.\r\n\r\nAs a result, every human endeavour can be reduced down to a process that flows through this system. NLP can be thought of as the process of modelling the flow of information through the nervous system. This flow produces behaviours and results.\r\n\r\nNLP is divided into 2 areas. The first area is fascinating and it is the second area that holds the real power and magic of NLP.\r\n\r\nThe first area is the area of behavioral modelling. This area is devoted to the discovery of the behavioural process of excellence. It asks the questions “How does a person do excellent behaviour?” “What does a person do with their nervous system to produce excellent results in a chosen field?”\r\n\r\nThese fields cover every area of human endeavour, from excellence in therapeutic interventions, accelerated learning, sporting excellence to sales and business mastery.\r\n\r\nThe second area (the real magic and power of NLP) turns this wealth of information retrieved in the first area into pure gold. This second area is a methodology for installing the very processes of excellence into another individual’s nervous system. Simply put, we now have the ability to install behaviour. If an individual would like to take on the behaviours and results of a top performer in any chosen field of endeavour, it is now possible through the processes of NLP.\r\n\r\nWhat behaviour of excellence would you like to achieve? Is it is sport, finance health, relationships, business or an area that is unique to you?', 'About NLP', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-nlp', '', '', '2015-01-09 06:27:28', '2015-01-09 06:27:28', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/?post_type=services&#038;p=98', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(99, 1, '2014-12-05 01:21:28', '2014-12-05 01:21:28', '<h4>Dynamic Mind Works is a team of Six</h4>\r\nOur team of six is lead by Robb Whitewood, original founder and director of Dynamic Mind Works Pty Ltd.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Robb Whitewood</span></h4>\r\nFounder &amp; Co-Director of Dynamic Mind Works.\r\n\r\nRobb Whitewood created Dynamic Mind Works in 1999. His vision is to assist as many people help as many people as he can. He would like to leave a legacy of ways to make life better for millions of individuals around the world. Robb Whitewood is a rare combination of trainer, entertainer and motivator.\r\n\r\nRobb has travelled the world since 16 and worked in many fields including acting and stunt acting within film and television. He has mastered Hynosis and NLP both as a trainer and as a clinician spanning over 25 years. He has studied and practised Chinese Medicine since the age of 15 and is highly qualified and skilled as an Acupuncturist and Diagnostician. He has been recently referred to as "The Gun" for his sharp shooting behavioural profiling skills within large corporate projects.\r\n\r\nRobb’s qualifications and achievements include:\r\n* Certified NLP Trainer\r\n* Certified Master Practitioner NLP\r\n* Certified Master Hypnotist\r\n* Certified Master Practitioner Time Based Therapy   (TBT)\r\n* Founder of Neuro Relationship Therapy (NRT)\r\n* Dip. Traditional Chinese Medicine (Acupuncture)\r\n* Founder of the Australian Board of NLP (ABNLP)\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Allison Low</span></h4>\r\nCo-Director &amp; Information Manager\r\n\r\nAllison joined Dynamic Mind Works in 2006. She completed her NLP Practitioner certification course with Richard Bandler the co-creator of NLP in 2004 in London, UK. Months later returning to Australia to complete the Master NLP Practitioner certification with Dynamic Mind Works.\r\n\r\nGraduated with Bachelor of Science, hons Psychology in 1992 and having completed a diploma in Remedial Massage in Australia in 1992 and also in England in 2004 along with EFT qualifications, she has a solid therapeutic foundation. Allison''s career path had been mapped out in Research in Behavioural Sciences but, her flair for Analytical Programming took her overseas from 1995. Travelling the world between 1997 and 2005 she visited over 30 countries and has worked in over 15 multi-national companies.\r\n\r\nAllison has a passion for moving Dynamic Mind Works into its next phase of adventure, exploring new ways of packaging well researched methodologies into Programs for the students and clients of Dynamic Mind Works. Allison is primarily responsible for the IT systems including website &amp; client databases.  Also overseeing internal workflow &amp; externally ensuring student satisfaction.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Jessica Roberts</span></h4>\r\nOffice Manager and PA to Robb Whitewood and Allison Low\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Matt Ryan</span></h4>\r\nStudent Training Co-ordinator\r\n\r\nBased at Bondi in Sydney''s eastern Suburbs, Matt has a lifelong interest in the power of language, psychology and Neuro Linguistic Programming. Having started his NLP training 8 years ago he has now achieved  the level of Trainer.\r\n\r\nAn established NLP therapist and coach, Matt has worked in the education field for the last 7 years. Helping many people find the right trainer has given him vast exposure to many different trainers and courses. He is extremely passionate about helping people find their own strengths and personal power.\r\n\r\nHaving an interest in the magic of the mind, scuba diving and living happy, Matt loves showing others how to create the changes they desire.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Niro Dayalan</span></h4>\r\nCoaching Program Manager\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Marcus Ferguson</span></h4>\r\nAssistant Trainer', 'Meet the Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'meet-the-team', '', '', '2015-01-12 08:36:38', '2015-01-12 08:36:38', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/?post_type=services&#038;p=99', 0, 'services', '', 0),
