(245, 1, '2015-01-03 08:21:23', '2015-01-03 08:21:23', '<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Current fees</span></h4>\r\nCurrent event fees are listed with the event information located by selecting your event from this <a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/event-calendar/">page</a>.\r\n\r\nOr visit the course page where the upcoming event is listed with the current fees for that course.   If there is no upcoming event listed, <a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">contact us</a> for a quote on the course you are interested in attending.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Events (1 hour to 1 day in length)</span></h4>\r\nPayment is required at the time of booking or on receiving the invoice.  In all cases fees settled before attendance of the event.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Courses longer than 1 day</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A 25% deposit  will be required within 4 days of booking your course too reserve your seat.</li>\r\n	<li>Full payment is required at least 14 days before your course begins.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Early Bird Offers</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Early bird offers have strict cut off dates for receiving payment.  If you miss paying the early bird amount by the cutoff date, the full price is applicable.  To be fair to all we do not extend early bird dates in any circumstances.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Payment Plans</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Payment installments available to approved students.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>3 month plan - 50% deposit received 14 days before course start.  3 equal installments over 3 months.  5% surcharge.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>6 month plan - 50 % deposit received 14 days before course start. 6 equal installments over 6 months.  7% surcharge.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>12 mth plan -50 % deposit received 14 days before course start. 12 equal installments over 12 months.  10% surcharge.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Finance</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Finance will become available through a reputable finance company during 2015.  The benefit is that you can attend your course now and pay later.  A small Dynamic Mind Works administration fee will be applicable.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">More information</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>For more information, please contact us today using the <a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">contact form.</a></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Fees settlement ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'fees-settlement', '', '', '2015-01-12 08:20:16', '2015-01-12 08:20:16', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/?page_id=245', 0, 'page', '', 0),
