(304, 1, '2015-01-07 03:37:41', '2015-01-07 03:37:41', 'Hi Allison\r\n\r\nI know how busy you both are, so thanks for replying. I hope you both and little Max are all well and that business is booming!\r\n\r\nI just had my first anniversary of living on my own in my new unit. It was a really tough year. My dad died, mum is ill, work is no longer enjoyable and most importantly learning to rely on myself, which was always a fear of mine.\r\n\r\nI mention these things as I really want to acknowledge the NLP programmes Rob ran. Without the skills I learned I would have found it much harder to cope and learn the lessons I needed to learn. I smile when I think how hard I fought Rob when he challenged my view of the world!\r\n\r\nI still have a long way to go and would like to do some more of your courses when I can. I notice you have moved to what looks like a great location.\r\n\r\nAnyway, thanks once again. I really want Rob to know that he changed my life for the better. People baulk at the cost of courses but if they knew how life-changing they can be, they would realise what an investment they are.\r\n\r\nCheers\r\n\r\nWendy.', 'Wendy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'wendy', '', '', '2015-01-11 02:12:42', '2015-01-11 02:12:42', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/?post_type=testimonials&#038;p=304', 0, 'testimonials', '', 0),
