(343, 1, '2015-01-12 08:50:17', '2015-01-12 08:50:17', '<p class="introduction2">Dynamic Mind Works is an Australian owned and operated propriety limited company. It has been operating as a provider of NLP education since 1980.  Dynamic Mind Works has was incorporated as a proprietry limited company in 1999.</p>\nRobb Whitewood is the founder of this company and is the director and principal trainer and clinician.  Dynamic Mind Works has worked with thousands of individuals and with over 30 small to large corporate entities.  Specialising in assisting both businesses and individuals to move forward through behavioural and thought pattern changing.  How?  A fusion of NLP, Hypnosis, Anchoring, and Eastern Philosophy.\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Our Mission</span></h4>\n<p class="introduction2">To offer the best value services and products to help committed individuals and companies to move ahead.</p>\nTo get the best outcome for every person and company who entrust their time and money with us.\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Our Team</span></h4>\n<p class="introduction2">Our team are passionate about what they do. They are all experienced in many facets of business and the personal journey of health, wealth and happiness.</p>\nOur core belief is about transparency and ethics.  Our pricing structure is fair and equal.  Matching the needs of each client with the appropriate service, course or product is a company code of conduct.\n\nThe team at Dynamic Mind Works are multi-talented and are united in developing an Australia-wide company that delivers better programs and services to more people.\n\nDynamic Mind Works self-manages all aspects of the business: administration, reception, marketing, training, and therapeutic services. As a team the challenge we face day to day is the balancing act of running the business smoothly on all fronts, all of the time.\n\nMeet our passionate team of six here!', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '58-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-12 08:50:17', '2015-01-12 08:50:17', '', 58, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/58-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(344, 1, '2015-01-09 06:16:49', '2015-01-09 06:16:49', '<h5 class="introduction2">About US</h5>\r\n<p class="introduction2">Dynamic Mind Works is an Australian owned and operated propriety limited company. It has been operating as a provider of NLP education since 1980.  Dynamic Mind Works has was incorporated as a proprietry limited company in 1999.</p>\r\nRobb Whitewood is the founder of this company and is the director and principal trainer and clinician.  Dynamic Mind Works has worked with thousands of individuals and with over 30 small to large corporate entities.  Specialising in assisting both businesses and individuals to move forward through behavioural and thought pattern changing.  How?  A fusion of NLP, Hypnosis, Anchoring, and Eastern Philosophy.\r\n<h4>Our Mission</h4>\r\n<p class="introduction2">To offer the best value services and products to help committed individuals and companies to move ahead.</p>\r\nTo get the best outcome for every person and company who entrust their time and money with us.\r\n<h4>Our Team</h4>\r\n<p class="introduction2">Our team are passionate about what they do. They are all experienced in many facets of business and the personal journey of health, wealth and happiness.</p>\r\nOur core belief is about transparency and ethics.  Our pricing structure is fair and equal.  Matching the needs of each client with the appropriate service, course or product is a company code of conduct.\r\n\r\nThe team at Dynamic Mind Works are multi-talented and are united in developing an Australia-wide company that delivers better programs and services to more people.\r\n\r\nDynamic Mind Works self-manages all aspects of the business: administration, reception, marketing, training, and therapeutic services. As a team the challenge we face day to day is the balancing act of running the business smoothly on all fronts, all of the time.\r\n<h6>Robb Whitewood - Principal trainer and clinician</h6>\r\nRobb Whitewood created Dynamic Mind Works in 1999. His vision is to assist as many people help as many people as he can. He would like to leave a legacy of ways to make life better for millions of individuals around the world. Robb Whitewood is a rare combination of trainer, entertainer and motivator. Robb has travelled the world since 16 and worked in many fields including acting and stunt acting within film and television. He has mastered Hynosis and NLP both as a trainer and as a clinician spanning over 25 years. He has studied and practised Chinese Medicine since the age of 15 and is highly qualified and skilled as an Acupunturist and Diagnostician. He has been recently referred to as "The Gun" for his sharp shooting behavioural profiling skills within large corporate''s projects.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h6>Allison Low - Information and Systems Manager</h6>\r\nAllison joined Dynamic Mind Works in 2006. She completed her NLP Practitioner certification course with Richard Bandler the co-creator of NLP in 2004 in London, UK. Months later returning to Australia to complete the Master NLP Practitioner certification with Dynamic Mind Works. Graduated with Bachelor of Science, hons Psychology in 1992 and having completed a diploma in Remedial Massage in Australia in 1992 and also in England in 2004 along with EFT qualifications, she has a solid therapeutic foundation. Allison''s career path had been mapped out in Research in Behavioural Sciences but, her flair for Analytical Programming took her overseas from 1995. Travelling the world between 1997 and 2005 she visited over 30 countries and has worked in over 15 multi-national companies. Allison has a passion for moving Dynamic Mind Works into its next phase of adventure, exploring new ways of packaging well researched methodologies into Programs for the students and clients of Dynamic Mind Works.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-09 06:16:49', '2015-01-09 06:16:49', '', 58, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/58-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
