(579, 1, '2015-01-12 08:45:55', '2015-01-12 08:45:55', 'NLP Enthusiasts take note!  Learn NLP from the comfort of your living room.\n\nIf you are interested in learning NLP but not interested in attending a full course just now for certification then why not purchase the full NLP DVD sets.\n\n<a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/nlp-dvd-set.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-385" src="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/nlp-dvd-set.jpg" alt="nlp-dvd-set" width="217" height="132" /></a>\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">NLP Practitioner DVD set</span></h4>\n<strong>22 disk DVD set - NLP Practitioner Certification.  $750 inc. GST\n</strong>\n\n<strong>37 hours of NLP training.  Live demonstrations, bonus techniques.</strong>\n\nThe pricing of this comprehensive DVD set reflects the volume of information included and the uniqueness of course content delivery.\n\nThe DVD set can be used in a variety of ways: a source of reference, learning, modelling, practice.  It is an educational resource and has been produced in a way to keep costs to a minimum so more customers can access this product.  Similar products on the market are priced at over $1,200.  <a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">Contact us to order.</a>\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">NLP Master Practitioner</span></h4>\n20 disk DVD set - Full classroom experience.  $950 inc. GST\n\nOver 44 hours of a real NLP Master Practitioner classroom training.\n\n<a href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/contact-us/">Contact us to order.</a>', 'NLP DVD sets', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '97-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-12 08:45:55', '2015-01-12 08:45:55', '', 97, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/97-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(580, 1, '2015-01-12 08:50:31', '2015-01-12 08:50:31', '<p class="introduction2">Dynamic Mind Works is an Australian owned and operated propriety limited company. It has been operating as a provider of NLP education since 1980.  Dynamic Mind Works has was incorporated as a proprietry limited company in 1999.</p>\r\nRobb Whitewood is the founder of this company and is the director and principal trainer and clinician.  Dynamic Mind Works has worked with thousands of individuals and with over 30 small to large corporate entities.  Specialising in assisting both businesses and individuals to move forward through behavioural and thought pattern changing.  How?  A fusion of NLP, Hypnosis, Anchoring, and Eastern Philosophy.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Our Mission</span></h4>\r\n<p class="introduction2">To offer the best value services and products to help committed individuals and companies to move ahead.</p>\r\nTo get the best outcome for every person and company who entrust their time and money with us.\r\n<h4><span style="color: #0000ff;">Our Team</span></h4>\r\n<p class="introduction2">Our team are passionate about what they do. They are all experienced in many facets of business and the personal journey of health, wealth and happiness.</p>\r\nOur core belief is about transparency and ethics.  Our pricing structure is fair and equal.  Matching the needs of each client with the appropriate service, course or product is a company code of conduct.\r\n\r\nThe team at Dynamic Mind Works are multi-talented and are united in developing an Australia-wide company that delivers better programs and services to more people.\r\n\r\nDynamic Mind Works self-manages all aspects of the business: administration, reception, marketing, training, and therapeutic services. As a team the challenge we face day to day is the balancing act of running the business smoothly on all fronts, all of the time.\r\n\r\n<a title="Meet the Team" href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/services/meet-the-team/">Meet our passionate team of six here!</a>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-12 08:50:31', '2015-01-12 08:50:31', '', 58, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/58-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(581, 1, '2015-01-12 09:05:12', '2015-01-12 09:05:12', '<h4>Connect with like minded people here.</h4>\nWith the launch of our new website we have a feature on a student that is the most divine human being!  She lives in North Eastern QLD and has extremely wonderful talents.  She graduated from the NLP Practitioner course in 2006 and the NLP Master Practitioner course in 2007.   Her other qualifications are extensive.  But what makes her special is her talents in living life in all its corners.\n\nWill you come back again very very soon to see the full feature article?', 'Featured Student', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-01-12 09:05:12', '2015-01-12 09:05:12', '', 92, 'http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/92-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
