(9, 9, 'course-categories', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Would you like to become a professional coach?</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Helping people improve their lives forever.  And by doing so change your life in the process?</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Would you like to make a significant change in the quality of the lives of those people around you?</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>How about helping people create and reach their dreams allowing people to realise their true potential.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe NLP Practitioner certification is a pre-requisite for attending this training.\r\n\r\nYour NLP Practitioner certification will have given you all of the primary skills required to help your clients remove barriers and install resourceful states. The Neuro Linguistic  Coach training puts a structure around your skills and teaches you the process of seeing clients in a professional setting.  You will have a career with elite skills in a growing industry.\r\n<h4>The four day training course will cover the following topics.</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Establishing rapport quickly (specifically for clinical application)</li>\r\n	<li>Developing your own hypnotic pre-talk.</li>\r\n	<li>Understanding the drama cycle as it relates to clinical practice</li>\r\n	<li>How to avoid mind reading</li>\r\n	<li>How to focus on content rather than content</li>\r\n	<li>Recognising transference and counter transference.</li>\r\n	<li>Formulas for working with:</li>\r\n	<li>Motivation</li>\r\n	<li>Goal setting</li>\r\n	<li>Financial issues</li>\r\n	<li>Relationship issue</li>\r\n	<li>Dealing with grief</li>\r\n	<li>Work Place issues</li>\r\n	<li>Creating Happiness</li>\r\n	<li>Depression busting</li>\r\n	<li>Phobias</li>\r\n	<li>Learning difficulties</li>\r\n	<li>Confidence</li>\r\n	<li>Exam preparation</li>\r\n	<li>Self Esteem</li>\r\n	<li>Metaphor design</li>\r\n	<li>Discovering well formed conditions</li>\r\n	<li>Getting leverage</li>\r\n	<li>Working within your skill sets.</li>\r\n	<li>Setting up a clinic</li>\r\n	<li>Finding clients</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>BONUSES:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Discounted Membership to relevant associations to qualify for the relevant insurance.</li>\r\n	<li>Receive a marketing pack with free and discounted advertising listings.</li>\r\n	<li>Templates for business cards, brochures &amp; website.</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, 25),
(10, 10, 'course-categories', '<h4>What is NLP?</h4>\r\nNLP, or Neuro Linguistic Programming, is the ability to affect or change the nervous system through the use of language. It is a process of observing how people carry out their behaviours and uncover the drivers behind thoughts. It’s not magic, but it may look that way to newcomers. In many ways, it is a doorway into another world of understanding and knowledge. It is the ability to expand personal awareness to the point of being able to positively influence both self and others with a sentence or gesture.\r\n<h4>Why NLP?</h4>\r\nYou will discover that there is no other training that gives you so many benefits. The long term benefits to your health, wealth and happiness will far outweigh the cost of your initial investment. Through our courses you will build an understanding of the inner workings of the human mind and nervous system, and how behaviour is controlled and created. These skills and techniques are readily applied in all areas of life, from the bedroom to the boardroom.\r\n<h4>Who is NLP for?</h4>\r\nNLP offers something for everyone! To any individual in positions that require that he or she influence the behaviour or thinking of others, like sales, marketing, teaching, business and law, it is essential learning. To the therapist/counsellor/coach, it is the difference between guessing and knowing the right thing to do to get that break-through or change of behaviour. To the natural therapist, it is a wonderful tool for bringing into alignment the mind and the body. To the parent, it is the operating manual for their child that was accidently left at the hospital. To you, it holds the power to transform your life and the lives of those around you.\r\n\r\nThis 8-day training covers 5 modules that will maximise your personal and professional outcomes:\r\n\r\n<strong>Module 1: Perception and Reality - The Doorway to Understanding</strong>\r\n\r\nHow an individual perceives reality is the blueprint of how they live life. A person’s perceptions determine the level of happiness, health, the quality and nature of their relationships. The individual that has understanding of this process can become the driver of life rather than the passenger.\r\n\r\nThis 2 day training is a look into the inner workings of the mind. How an individual creates reality is a complex process of experiential filters, memories, and decisions. These unconscious processes produce emotions that drive behaviour and in turn produce results. As a person changes their perceptions on the inside of their head, the outside world of reality soon follows.\r\n\r\n<strong>Communication Mastery  - The Key to Dealing with Others.</strong>\r\n\r\nCommunication Mastery deals with how people communicate at a neurological level. This training weekend is for gaining tremendous understanding of how people actually communicate and apply it. It is important to know how to generate those magical moments of deep rapport that form the foundation of great relationships, whether these relationships be of a personal or professional nature.  For the professional, greater communication skills relate directly to increased profitability.\r\n\r\nCommunication is also a key to happier, healthier and more productive personal relationships. Past participants report tremendous improvement in the quality of their family lives by understanding and applying simple communication patterns. Most notable is the change in the quality of relationship with their children.\r\n\r\n<strong>Techniques for Success -  Fundamentals-Tools for Changing the fabric of life.</strong>\r\n\r\nWhen combined with “Perception and Reality” &amp; “Communication Mastery” this  2 day module becomes the final instalment of the core material for the NLP Practitioner certification. It is 2 days packed with powerful proven techniques for personal and professional change.\r\n\r\n“Techniques for Success” is designed to allow the individual to experience and demonstrate the life changing techniques of NLP. Trigger powerful motivational states in oneself and others. Destroy limiting beliefs. Change old patterns, habits and beliefs into new patterns for success. Replicate the behaviours of your role models to attain new life changing ways. “Techniques for Success” is literally learning how to rewire the mind to produce new habits and ways of thinking.\r\n\r\n<strong>BONUS Module: NLP Magic - The art of making BIG problems Disappear.\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Includes </em>Time Based Technique &amp; Neuro-Relationship Technique (created by Robb Whitewood and only taught in this school).\r\n\r\nNLP Magic includes two powerful NLP styled techniques. The first is based on how the individual processes time (Time Based Techniques - TBT). The second is based on how the individual stores relationships in their mind (Neuro Relationship Techniques - NRT). Understanding and utilising these two techniques allows you to communicate and be effective at all levels with any individual.\r\n\r\nNLP Magic is a system of dissolving negative emotion, limiting decisions and complex relationship issues. These two systems are taught together for the simple reason that emotions and relationships shape our present moments. These present moments make up how an individual sees the world and as a result how they feel and act. When feelings and relationships are out of sync, all sorts of behavioural, physical and psychological problems surface.\r\n\r\n<strong>Who will benefit from this module? </strong>These technologies are not just for the Psychologist, Counselor, Coach or Hypnotherapist. Anyone has the ability to learn and use these techniques with competence. Strange as it may seem, many Business people are using these techniques to increase their team’s performance.\r\n\r\n<strong>BONUS Module: Hypnosis - The Doorway to Another World </strong>\r\n\r\nHypnosis training is a vital tool in the toolbox of life.  In today’s hectic pace, it is essential that we develop skills of the mind. The 21st century is full of stress inducing situations that an ancient time tested skill can easily deal with.  Hypnosis is easy to learn and gives great insight into the workings of the mind. As a skill it can be used to help solve many problems by simply bypassing the conscious mind and taking us straight to the unconscious. Because the unconscious is the warehouse of emotions and behaviours, tremendous change is possible to produce incredible results. This ability is vital to any individual that wants to make a change in their lives. It can be used to remove past pain or just show us the way to a great future.\r\n<h4>What''s included?</h4>\r\n<div id="wp-tabs-1" class="wp-tabs wpui-narrow wpui-styles">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>8 days of face to face training with practical hands-on experience</li>\r\n	<li>Access to over 50 Dynamic Mind Work’s NLP video educational clips</li>\r\n	<li>An NLP Introduction DVD with rights to copy 10 times to give away</li>\r\n	<li>Access to your trainer before and after your course</li>\r\n	<li>Heavily Discounted NLP DVD sets</li>\r\n	<li>Course Refresh options at <a title="Fees settlement" href="http://111.93.163.218/Robbwhitewood/php/fees-settlement/">discounted rates</a></li>\r\n	<li>Complimentary pre-training consultation with your trainer to align your needs to the course.</li>\r\n	<li>An NLP Practitioner certification recognised by the AANLP &amp; IICT.com.au</li>\r\n	<li>Additionally you are awarded with a Hypnosis, Time Based Technique and Neuro-Relationship Technique certificate.</li>\r\n	<li>Option to sit an NLP online examination.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>As a direct result of taking this course, your outcomes will be:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Learn and utilise the full set of NLP foundation techniques</li>\r\n	<li>Learn and utlise Hypnosis, Neuro Relationship Technique and Time Based Technique.</li>\r\n	<li>Understand how to plug-in these techniques to personal and professional situations</li>\r\n	<li>Tidy your own values, beliefs and history</li>\r\n	<li>Align your goals and your values for instant motivation</li>\r\n	<li>Realise your true personal potential</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 0, 57),
(11, 11, 'course-categories', '<h4>What is NLP Master Practitioner Certification?</h4>\r\nOne student described it as the missing operating manual for the human mind. In many ways, it is a doorway into another world of understanding and knowledge. It is the ability to expand personal awareness to the point of being able to positively influence both self and others with a sentence or gesture.\r\n\r\nEach individual who undertakes NLP Master Practitioner Certification will have a different application for the training. NLP Master Practitioner is about understanding the inner workings of the human mind and nervous system, and how behavior is controlled and created. This practical knowledge and the accompanying skills and techniques are essential for those in positions of responsibility or leadership (or who aspire to be).\r\n\r\nIt is essential learning for any individual in positions that require that he or she influence the behaviour or thinking of others, like sales, marketing, teaching, business and law.\r\n\r\nTo the therapist, counsellor, coach, it is the difference between <em>guessing</em> and <em>knowing</em> the right thing to do to get that break-through or change of behaviour. To the natural therapist, it is a wonderful tool for bringing into alignment the mind and the body.\r\n\r\nTo the parent, it is the operating manual that was accidentally left at the hospital.\r\n<h4>For everyone, it is a journey of self-discovery that leads to life contentment.</h4>\r\nYour Master NLP practitioner course is facilitated by Robb Whitewood, one of only a handful of highly experienced NLP trainers operating in Australia today. This NLP certification course is taught to international standards and is recognised all over the world. This 12-day training covers 4 modules that will maximise your personal and professional outcomes.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Quantum Change Advanced NLP techniques</li>\r\n	<li>BONUS Module: Advanced Hypnosis</li>\r\n	<li>BONUS Module: Advanced NLP Magic incorporating\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Advanced Time Based Technique.</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Neuro-Relationship Technique.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><strong>Your course will include:</strong></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>12 days of face to face training – practical hands-on experience.</li>\r\n	<li>Heavily discounted Master NLP DVD sets, unique to Dynamic Mind Works</li>\r\n	<li>Access to a library of over 50 online NLP educational video clips</li>\r\n	<li>Access to your trainer after your course in the form of monthly webinar.</li>\r\n	<li>Course Refresh options at discounted rates</li>\r\n	<li>Complimentary pre-training consultation with your trainer to align your needs to the course</li>\r\n	<li>BONUS topic: Advanced NRT, a powerful relationship focussed technique to address relationship issues and support healthy relationship constructs (NRT was designed by Robb Whitewood and only taught in this school)</li>\r\n	<li>Option to sit an Master NLP online examination.</li>\r\n	<li>A Master NLP Practitioner certification recognised by the AANLP and IICT.</li>\r\n	<li>Additionally you are awarded with a Advanced: Hypnosis, Time Based Technique and Neuro-Relationship Technique certificates</li>\r\n	<li>On graduation you qualify to join the NLP Trainer Training course.</li>\r\n</ul>', 0, 34),
